- `generateMonthlyReview` (message content, band gap, vocabulary mastery, edge cases)
- `checkAndGenerate` (both due, only weekly, only monthly, schedule updates, storage, event bus)
- `forceWeeklyReview` / `forceMonthlyReview` (generation, storage, event bus)
- Edge cases (zero values, empty weak skills, singular/plural grammar)

All 74 tests pass. No regressions in existing tests. No type errors added.
